      "type": "Annotation",
      "body": [
        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "purpose": "transcribing",
          "value": "MI CHAMOCHAH ba-eilim, Adonai!\nMi kamochah nedar bakodesh,\nnora t'hilot, oseih fele!\nMalchut'cha ra-u vanecha,\nbokei-a yam lifnei Moshe uMiryam.\nZeh Eli, anu v'amru,\nAdonai yimloch l'olam va-ed!\nV'ne-emar: ki fadah Adonai et Yaakov,\nug'alo miyad chazak mimenu.\nBaruch atah, Adonai, gaal Yisrael.",
          "language": "en"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-07-12T22:28:15.818Z",
